cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a method to estimate a certain aspect of the forward kinematics model for a robot.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques to automatically discover the robot kinematics.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possibility as the paper mentions the use of exteroceptive data flow, which could include visual data.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper proposes a method to generate an internal representation of the end-effector configuration from data flow.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper mentions the use of a mapping from the proprioceptive space to the representational space to control the robot.
